<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[كَظَرَ]</span> القَوْسَ: إِذا جعل فيها كُظْراً) <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[م]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[كَظَمَ]</span>: غيظَه كظماً: إِذا سكت عليه ولم يُظهره،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَالْكااظِمِينَ الْغَيْظَ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والكُظوم:</span> السُّكوت.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والكُظوم:</span> إِمساك البعير جِرَّتَه،<span class="c5"> يقال:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>كظم البعير جِرَّتَه. وبعيرٌ كَاظم،<span class="c5"> وإِبلٌ كُظوم:</span> إِذا لم تجترّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والمكظوم:</span> المكروب.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
